                    "text": "<p>Our workshop sits in the hills of Vermont, where the rhythm of the seasons shapes everything we make. Here, leather is hand-dyed in small vats, candles are poured by feel not formula, and every soap bar is cut from a loaf by the same hands that mixed the botanicals. We do not chase perfection — we chase character. The slight variation in grain, the gentle imperfection of a hand-rolled edge: these are not flaws, they are signatures.</p>",
